The project now runs as C++ code and is compiled using the C++ compiler. 
Everything is rendered on the screen using ncurses. 
Fog of war is implemented. To turn it off press f, then once you move the player, the fog of war turns back on.
When the player waants to teleport. Player presses t, moves the player and a cursor appears. Moves the player to any point in the dungeon. However, it does not move the player to a monster or to a rock position.

